      <title>莱特称防御性股票比追逐动能股票更好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/defensive-stocks-better-than-chasing-momentum-lait-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Latitude Investment Management 的管理合伙人弗雷迪·莱特 (Freddie Lait) 表示，股市将迎来一个“动荡或动荡的夏天”。他在彭博电视台发表讲话时表示，投资“防御性”并继续实现强劲增长率的股票比“追逐势头”要好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/defensive-stocks-better-than-chasing-momentum-lait-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
